<p>
  <a href="/guides/web-content/create-a-page">Custom pages</a> can contain
  variables that are replaced with values when the page is presented to a visitor.
</p>

<p>Variables are designated in the page body using the following syntax:</p>

<pre>
<code class="language-html" data-lang="html">
  {{ VARIABLE_NAME }}
</code>
</pre>

