<h3>Example</h3>

<p>
  To display the company name defined in
  <a href="/guides/settings">Admin Settings</a>,
  use the following code:
</p>

<pre>
<code class="language-html" data-lang="html">
  Welcome to the {{ company_name }} website!
</code>
</pre>

<p>
  Assuming <em>company_name</em> is defined as "Acme, Inc.", a visitor will be
  presented with the following:
</p>

<pre>
<code>
  Welcome to the Acme, Inc. website!
</code>
</pre>
